{"tid":1540493,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"太子CCTV！唔好比「撤回」轉移視線","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T15:41:55.000Z","uid":120729,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6c5b5f8af0755d568c24a6e00af950228b85a7b0","tid":1540493,"uid":120729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:38:33.000Z","msg":"到底831嗰日發生咗啲乜事<br />\n有冇人死咗喺入邊<br />\n警察點樣用武力對待示威者<br />\n我哋要真相 要當日太子CCTV！<br />\n可唔可以停止討論佢撤回啲野啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFocus返警察濫權 太子站 受傷人士到<br />\n點解嗌咗句「你哋個良心去咗邊」可以成班防暴衝上去打人拉人？<br />\n點解警察可以無差別打人？<br />\n點解警察會拖行傷者，令到傷者情況惡化？<br />\n點解無警告下開槍？<br />\n點解要扮示威者掟汽油彈？<br />\n點解要插贓嫁禍示威者？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n點解警察扮示威者可以帶槍仲要開咗2發？<br />\n</span><br />\n點解太子站當日唔比first aid 記者入？<br />\n點解警察可以阻住first aid救人？<br />\n仲有好多個點解 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千祈唔好習慣咗佢哋咁做</span><br />\n我哋個唔應該將個焦點放喺撤回到（對外國文宣另計）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/he82uG9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhe82uG9.jpg&h=abd496e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"100b31dcb4a0c560a1fa5a7f0a2759e89ce95357","tid":1540493,"uid":120729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:39:28.000Z","msg":"點解警察扮示威者可以帶槍仲要開咗2槍？！"},{"pid":"50082e745e2f2e63c36176c645d41f9b4ff1b963","tid":1540493,"uid":250508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:39:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"217933273c867155a2aaf0d1bf8eeb4d701c269d","tid":1540493,"uid":120729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:40:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請黨鐵公開831太子CCTV</span>"},{"pid":"9d38551e6ad0a90b4ea285df2179506a8b0f9364","tid":1540493,"uid":92643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:40:15.000Z","msg":"推呀!要CCTV,屌你老母"},{"pid":"7d773b78643aa7b8c7bc0250660f88fccb3ee9d9","tid":1540493,"uid":120729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,